OL,3,CPedestrian seriously injured after
OL,4,Cbeing hit by car
OL,6,FA 74-year-old woman has been seriously
OL,7,Finjured after she was hit by a car in
OL,8,Fthe West Sussex village of Plaistow.
OL,10,FThe collision occurred just after
OL,11,Fmidday on Saturday May 2nd on Loxwood
OL,12,FRoad.
OL,14,FThe victim, a local woman, was taken
OL,15,Fto hospital for treatment.
OL,17,FSgt Mark Miller said: "We are actively
OL,18,Finvestigating the circumstances of
OL,19,Fthis serious collision, which involved
OL,20,Fa green convertible BMW Z.
